EmpathP  is a producer and an illustrator. Other than producing VOCALOID works, she also produces UTAU and utaite works. She collaborates occasionally with other producers. She is also known as the illustrator of the VOCALOID3 voicebank Avanna, and the provider for the VOCALOID4 voicebank DAINA.
